{{ ->property }} Anadditionalnoteaboutarrayexpressions:Takenotethat`@foo.@bar`isastringconcatenation`$foo.$bar`),whereas`@foo.bar`translatesto`$foo['bar']`.If`$foo[$bar]`iswhatyouintended,usethe`@foo[@bar]`regularnotation.

Frameworkvariablesmayalsocontainanonymousfunctions:

```php
$f3->set('func',
function($a,$b){
return$a.','.$b;
}
);
